      <title>对冲基金 Vantage Point 买入美元和日本股票，押注特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/hedge-fund-buys-dollar-japan-stocks-in-bet-on-trump-landslide</link>
